// ============non-terminal types=============
//  # => Integer
//  <assign> => Statement
//  <case> => Statement
//  <case>* => List<Statement>
//  <class decl> => ClassDecl
//  <class decl>+ => List<ClassDecl>
//  <decl in class> => Decl
//  <decl in class>* => List<Decl>
//  <empty bracket pair> => Object
//  <empty bracket pair>* => List<Object>
//  <empty bracket pair>** => List<Object>
//  <exp1> => Exp
//  <exp2> => Exp
//  <exp3> => Exp
//  <exp4> => Exp
//  <exp5> => Exp
//  <exp6> => Exp
//  <exp7> => Exp
//  <exp8> => Exp
//  <exp> => Exp
//  <expList> => ExpList
//  <formalList> => VarDeclList
//  <inst var decl> => Decl
//  <listElement> => VarDecl
//  <listElement>* => List<VarDecl>
//  <local var decl> => Statement
//  <method decl> => Decl
//  <methodCall> => Call
//  <next exp> => Exp
//  <next exp>* => List<Exp>
//  <program> => Program
//  <returnStmt> => Exp
//  <start> => void
//  <stmt> => Statement
//  <stmt>* => List<Statement>
//  <type> => Type
//  CHARLIT => Integer
//  ID => String
//  INTLIT => Integer
//  STRINGLIT => String
//  `! => void
//  `!= => void
//  `% => void
//  `&& => void
//  `( => void
//  `) => void
//  `* => void
//  `+ => void
//  `++ => void
//  `, => void
//  `- => void
//  `-- => void
//  `. => void
//  `/ => void
//  `: => void
//  `; => void
//  `< => void
//  `<= => void
//  `= => void
//  `== => void
//  `> => void
//  `>= => void
//  `[ => void
//  `] => void
//  `abstract => void
//  `assert => void
//  `boolean => void
//  `break => void
//  `byte => void
//  `case => void
//  `catch => void
//  `char => void
//  `class => void
//  `const => void
//  `continue => void
//  `default => void
//  `do => void
//  `double => void
//  `else => void
//  `enum => void
//  `extends => void
//  `false => void
//  `final => void
//  `finally => void
//  `float => void
//  `for => void
//  `goto => void
//  `if => void
//  `implements => void
//  `import => void
//  `instanceof => void
//  `int => void
//  `interface => void
//  `long => void
//  `native => void
//  `new => void
//  `null => void
//  `package => void
//  `private => void
//  `protected => void
//  `public => void
//  `return => void
//  `short => void
//  `static => void
//  `strictfp => void
//  `super => void
//  `switch => void
//  `synchronized => void
//  `this => void
//  `throw => void
//  `throws => void
//  `transient => void
//  `true => void
//  `try => void
//  `void => void
//  `volatile => void
//  `while => void
//  `{ => void
//  `|| => void
//  `} => void
//  any => Character
//  any* => List<Character>
//  any128 => Character
//  digit => Character
//  digit* => List<Character>
//  digit128 => Character
//  hexDigit => Character
//  hexDigit* => List<Character>
//  hexDigit128 => Character
//  idChar => Character
//  idChar* => List<Character>
//  idChar128 => Character
//  letter => Character
//  letter128 => Character
//  registerNewline => void
//  ws => void
//  ws* => void
// ============productions (after empty-removal)=============
// 0: $$start ::= <start>
// 1: <start> ::= ws* <program>
// 2: <start> ::= <program>
// 3: <program> ::= <class decl>+
// 4: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 5: <class decl> ::= `class ID `{ `}
// 6: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `}
// 7: <class decl> ::= `class ID `extends ID `{ `}
// 8: <decl in class> ::= <method decl>
// 9: <decl in class> ::= <inst var decl>
// 10: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* `}
// 11: <method decl> ::= `public `void ID <formalList> `{ `}
// 12: <method decl> ::= `public !`void <type> ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* <returnStmt> `}
// 13: <method decl> ::= `public !`void <type> ID <formalList> `{ <returnStmt> `}
// 14: <returnStmt> ::= `return <exp> `;
// 15: <formalList> ::= `( <type> ID <listElement>* `)
// 16: <formalList> ::= `( <type> ID `)
// 17: <formalList> ::= `( `)
// 18: <listElement> ::= `, <type> ID
// 19: <type> ::= `int
// 20: <type> ::= `boolean
// 21: <type> ::= `void
// 22: <type> ::= `null
// 23: <type> ::= ID
// 24: <type> ::= <type> <empty bracket pair>
// 25: <empty bracket pair> ::= `[ `]
// 26: <stmt> ::= `{ <stmt>* `}
// 27: <stmt> ::= `{ `}
// 28: <stmt> ::= <assign> `;
// 29: <stmt> ::= <local var decl> `;
// 30: <stmt> ::= <methodCall> `;
// 31: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> !`else
// 32: <stmt> ::= `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> `else <stmt>
// 33: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; <exp> `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 34: <stmt> ::= `for `( <assign> `; `; <assign> `) <stmt>
// 35: <stmt> ::= `while `( <exp> `) <stmt>
// 36: <stmt> ::= `break `;
// 37: <assign> ::= <exp> `= <exp>
// 38: <assign> ::= ID `++
// 39: <assign> ::= `++ ID
// 40: <assign> ::= ID `--
// 41: <assign> ::= `-- ID
// 42: <local var decl> ::= <type> ID `= <exp>
// 43: <inst var decl> ::= <type> ID `;
// 44: <stmt> ::= `;
// 45: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ <case>* `}
// 46: <stmt> ::= `switch `( <exp> `) `{ `}
// 47: <case> ::= `case <exp> `:
// 48: <case> ::= <stmt>
// 49: <case> ::= `default `:
// 50: <exp> ::= <exp8>
// 51: <exp8> ::= <exp7>
// 52: <exp7> ::= <exp6>
// 53: <exp6> ::= <exp5>
// 54: <exp5> ::= <exp4>
// 55: <exp4> ::= <exp3>
// 56: <exp3> ::= <exp2>
// 57: <exp2> ::= <exp1>
// 58: <exp8> ::= <exp8> `|| <exp7>
// 59: <exp7> ::= <exp7> `&& <exp6>
// 60: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `== <exp5>
// 61: <exp6> ::= <exp6> `!= <exp5>
// 62: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `< <exp4>
// 63: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `<= <exp4>
// 64: <exp5> ::= <exp5> `> <exp4>
// 65: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `+ <exp3>
// 66: <exp4> ::= <exp4> `- <exp3>
// 67: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `* <exp2>
// 68: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `/ <exp2>
// 69: <exp3> ::= <exp3> `% <exp2>
// 70: <exp2> ::= `( <type> `) <exp1>
// 71: <exp2> ::= `+ <exp1>
// 72: <exp2> ::= `- <exp1>
// 73: <exp2> ::= `! <exp1>
// 74: <exp1> ::= ID
// 75: <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `]
// 76: <exp1> ::= INTLIT
// 77: <exp1> ::= STRINGLIT
// 78: <exp1> ::= CHARLIT
// 79: <exp1> ::= <exp1> `. ID
// 80: <exp1> ::= `this
// 81: <exp1> ::= `true
// 82: <exp1> ::= `false
// 83: <exp1> ::= `null
// 84: <exp1> ::= `new ID `( `)
// 85: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] <empty bracket pair>**
// 86: <exp1> ::= `new <type> !<empty bracket pair> `[ <exp> `] !<empty bracket pair>
// 87: <expList> ::= <exp> <next exp>*
// 88: <expList> ::= <exp>
// 89: <next exp> ::= `, <exp>
// 90: <methodCall> ::= <exp1> `. ID `( <expList> `)
// 91: <methodCall> ::= <exp1> `. ID `( `)
// 92: <methodCall> ::= `super `. ID `( <expList> `)
// 93: <methodCall> ::= `super `. ID `( `)
// 94: <methodCall> ::= ID `( <expList> `)
// 95: <methodCall> ::= ID `( `)
// 96: letter ::= {"A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 97: letter128 ::= {193..218 225..250}
// 98: digit ::= {"0".."9"}
// 99: digit128 ::= {176..185}
// 100: any ::= {0..127}
// 101: any128 ::= {128..255}
// 102: ws ::= " "
// 103: ws ::= {10}
// 104: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o" ws*
// 105: `boolean ::= "#" "b" "o"
// 106: `class ::= "#" "c" "l" ws*
// 107: `class ::= "#" "c" "l"
// 108: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x" ws*
// 109: `extends ::= "#" "e" "x"
// 110: `void ::= "#" "v" "o" ws*
// 111: `void ::= "#" "v" "o"
// 112: `int ::= "#" "i" "t" ws*
// 113: `int ::= "#" "i" "t"
// 114: `while ::= "#" "w" "h" ws*
// 115: `while ::= "#" "w" "h"
// 116: `if ::= "#" "+" ws*
// 117: `if ::= "#" "+"
// 118: `else ::= "#" "e" "l" ws*
// 119: `else ::= "#" "e" "l"
// 120: `for ::= "#" "f" "o" ws*
// 121: `for ::= "#" "f" "o"
// 122: `break ::= "#" "b" "r" ws*
// 123: `break ::= "#" "b" "r"
// 124: `this ::= "#" "t" "h" ws*
// 125: `this ::= "#" "t" "h"
// 126: `false ::= "#" "f" "a" ws*
// 127: `false ::= "#" "f" "a"
// 128: `true ::= "#" "t" "r" ws*
// 129: `true ::= "#" "t" "r"
// 130: `super ::= "#" "s" "u" ws*
// 131: `super ::= "#" "s" "u"
// 132: `null ::= "#" "n" "u" ws*
// 133: `null ::= "#" "n" "u"
// 134: `return ::= "#" "r" "e" ws*
// 135: `return ::= "#" "r" "e"
// 136: `new ::= "#" "n" "e" ws*
// 137: `new ::= "#" "n" "e"
// 138: `case ::= "#" "c" "e" ws*
// 139: `case ::= "#" "c" "e"
// 140: `default ::= "#" "d" "e" ws*
// 141: `default ::= "#" "d" "e"
// 142: `public ::= "#" "p" "u" ws*
// 143: `public ::= "#" "p" "u"
// 144: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w" ws*
// 145: `switch ::= "#" "s" "w"
// 146: `! ::= "!" ws*
// 147: `! ::= "!"
// 148: `!= ::= "@" "!" ws*
// 149: `!= ::= "@" "!"
// 150: `% ::= "%" ws*
// 151: `% ::= "%"
// 152: `&& ::= "@" "&" ws*
// 153: `&& ::= "@" "&"
// 154: `* ::= "*" ws*
// 155: `* ::= "*"
// 156: `( ::= "(" ws*
// 157: `( ::= "("
// 158: `) ::= ")" ws*
// 159: `) ::= ")"
// 160: `{ ::= "{" ws*
// 161: `{ ::= "{"
// 162: `} ::= "}" ws*
// 163: `} ::= "}"
// 164: `- ::= "-" ws*
// 165: `- ::= "-"
// 166: `+ ::= "+" ws*
// 167: `+ ::= "+"
// 168: `= ::= "=" ws*
// 169: `= ::= "="
// 170: `== ::= "@" "=" ws*
// 171: `== ::= "@" "="
// 172: `[ ::= "[" ws*
// 173: `[ ::= "["
// 174: `] ::= "]" ws*
// 175: `] ::= "]"
// 176: `|| ::= "@" "|" ws*
// 177: `|| ::= "@" "|"
// 178: `< ::= "<" ws*
// 179: `< ::= "<"
// 180: `<= ::= "@" "<" ws*
// 181: `<= ::= "@" "<"
// 182: `, ::= "," ws*
// 183: `, ::= ","
// 184: `> ::= ">" !"=" ws*
// 185: `> ::= ">" !"="
// 186: `: ::= ":" ws*
// 187: `: ::= ":"
// 188: `. ::= "." ws*
// 189: `. ::= "."
// 190: `; ::= ";" ws*
// 191: `; ::= ";"
// 192: `++ ::= "@" "+" ws*
// 193: `++ ::= "@" "+"
// 194: `-- ::= "@" "-" ws*
// 195: `-- ::= "@" "-"
// 196: `/ ::= "/" ws*
// 197: `/ ::= "/"
// 198: ID ::= letter128 ws*
// 199: ID ::= letter128
// 200: ID ::= letter idChar* $$0
// 201: ID ::= letter $$0
// 202: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} digit* $$1
// 203: INTLIT ::= {"1".."9"} $$1

// 205: INTLIT ::= digit128
// 206: INTLIT ::= "0" hexDigit* $$2
// 207: INTLIT ::= "0" $$2
// 208: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"' ws*
// 209: STRINGLIT ::= "@" '"'
// 210: STRINGLIT ::= '"' any* $$3
// 211: STRINGLIT ::= '"' $$3
// 212: CHARLIT ::= "'" any ws*
// 213: CHARLIT ::= "'" any
// 214: idChar ::= letter
// 215: idChar ::= digit

// 220: hexDigit ::= {"0".."9" "A".."Z" "a".."z"}
// 221: hexDigit128 ::= {176..185 193..198 225..230}
// 222: digit* ::= digit* digit
// 223: digit* ::= digit
// 224: <next exp>* ::= <next exp>* <next exp>
// 225: <next exp>* ::= <next exp>
// 226: any* ::= any* any
// 227: any* ::= any
// 228: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>* <decl in class>
// 229: <decl in class>* ::= <decl in class>
// 230: <listElement>* ::= <listElement>* <listElement>
// 231: <listElement>* ::= <listElement>
// 232: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit* hexDigit
// 233: hexDigit* ::= hexDigit
// 234: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>* <stmt>
// 235: <stmt>* ::= <stmt>
// 236: <case>* ::= <case>* <case>
// 237: <case>* ::= <case>
// 238: idChar* ::= idChar* idChar
// 239: idChar* ::= idChar
// 240: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>
// 241: <class decl>+ ::= <class decl>+ <class decl>
// 242: <empty bracket pair>** ::= <empty bracket pair>* !<empty bracket pair>
// 243: ws* ::= ws* ws
// 244: ws* ::= ws
// 245: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>* <empty bracket pair>
// 246: <empty bracket pair>* ::= <empty bracket pair>
// 247: $$0 ::= idChar128 ws*
// 248: $$0 ::= idChar128
// 249: $$1 ::= digit128 ws*
// 250: $$1 ::= digit128
// 251: $$2 ::= hexDigit128 ws*
// 252: $$2 ::= hexDigit128
// 253: $$3 ::= any128 ws*
// 254: $$3 ::= any128

**** STATE 0 ****
    $$start ::= <%> <start> // $
    -----------------------
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // $
    <class decl> ::= <%> `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] `} // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl> // <class decl>
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // $
    <class decl>+ ::= <%> <class decl>+ <class decl> // <class decl>
    <program> ::= [#] <%> <class decl>+ // $
    <start> ::= <%> ws* <program> // $
    <start> ::= [ws*] <%> <program> // $
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" [ws*] // ID
    `class ::= <%> "#" "c" "l" ws* // ID
    ws ::= <%> " " // <program>
    ws ::= <%> " " // ws
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // <program>
    ws ::= <%> {10} [registerNewline] // ws
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // <program>
    ws* ::= <%> ws* ws // ws
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // <program>
    ws* ::= [ws*] <%> ws // ws
        <class decl>+ => shift: 68
        "#" => shift: 498
        ws => shift: 671
        <program> => shift: 229
        `class => shift: 32
        <start> => shift: 686
        ws* => shift: 368
        {10} => shift: 29
        " " => shift: 107
        <class decl> => shift: 669
**** STATE 1 ****
    -----------------------
**** STATE 2 ****
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // <next exp>
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // <next exp>*
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `&&
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `)
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `*
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `+
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `-
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `.
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `/
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `:
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `;
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `<=
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `=
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `==
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `>
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[
    ws ::= {10} !<empty bracket pair> [registerNewline] <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `]

**** STATE 299 ****
    <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> [#] `[ <exp> <%> `] !<empty bracket pair> // `[
    <exp1> ::= <exp1> !<empty bracket pair> [#] `[ <exp> <%> `] // <next exp>

    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `if `( <exp> `) <stmt> [#] `else <stmt> // `}
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `switch `( <exp> `) `{ <case>* `} // <case>

    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `while `( <exp> `) <stmt> // `}
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `{ <stmt>* `} // <case>
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `{ <stmt>* `} // `}
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `{ [<stmt>*] `} // <case>
    <stmt> ::= [#] <%> `{ [<stmt>*] `} // `}

**** STATE 362 ****
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] <%> `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `{ [<decl in class>*] <%> `} // <class decl>
    -----------------------
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // `}
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // `}
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // <decl in class>
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* <returnStmt> `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* <returnStmt> `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] <returnStmt> `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] <returnStmt> `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] `} // `}
    <type> ::= [#] <%> <type> <empty bracket pair> // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> <type> <empty bracket pair> // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> ID // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> ID // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `boolean // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `boolean // ID
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `int // <empty bracket pair>
    <type> ::= [#] <%> `int // ID

    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ <%> <decl in class>* `} // <class decl>
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] <%> `} // $
    <class decl> ::= `class [#] ID `extends ID `{ [<decl in class>*] <%> `} // <class decl>
    -----------------------
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <inst var decl> // `}
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class> ::= <%> <method decl> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= <%> <decl in class>* <decl in class> // `}
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // <decl in class>
    <decl in class>* ::= [<decl in class>*] <%> <decl in class> // `}
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // <decl in class>
    <inst var decl> ::= <%> <type> [#] ID `; // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* <returnStmt> `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* <returnStmt> `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] <returnStmt> `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public !`void <type> [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] <returnStmt> `} // `}
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* `} // <decl in class>
    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ <stmt>* `} // `}

    <method decl> ::= <%> `public `void [#] ID <formalList> `{ [<stmt>*] `} // `}

        {176..185} => shift: 54
        {"1".."9"} => shift: 156
        STRINGLIT => shift: 154
        letter128 => shift: 565

    `[ ::= "[" <%> ws* // <exp>
    `[ ::= "[" <%> ws* // `]
    `[ ::= "[" [ws*] <%> // <exp>
    `[ ::= "[" [ws*] <%> // `]
    -----------------------
    ws ::= <%> " " // <exp>
    ws ::= <%> " " // `]

    ID ::= letter128 ws* !<empty bracket pair> <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `[
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // <next exp>
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // <next exp>*
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // ID
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `!=
    ID ::= letter128 ws* <!<empty bracket pair>%> // `%

        {176..185} => shift: 54
        <local var decl> => shift: 685
        {"1".."9"} => shift: 156
        STRINGLIT => shift: 154
        letter128 => shift: 565
        "-" => shift: 557
        `; => shift: 101
        `while => shift: 396
        "!" => shift: 100
        `if => shift: 284
